    "26 aimed to improve the automated evaluation of divergent thinking tasks by fine-tuning LLMs on human-evaluated responses.",
    "The study showed a significant advancement compared to conventional semantic distance methods, as the LLMs' assessments were found to be more in line with human judgments.",
    "This finding underscores the potential of LLMs to accurately gauge creative thinking abilities.",
